com.vmware.vcenter.hvc.management

Interface Administrators

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AdministratorsTypes, com.vmware.vapi.bindings.Service
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdministratorsStub

    public interface Administrators
extends com.vmware.vapi.bindings.Service, AdministratorsTypes
    The Administrators provides methods to update, delete, and list groups in the local sso group. This is limited to the Hybrid Linked Mode service. Usage beyond VMware Cloud on AWS is not supported.

    • Field Summary

      • Fields inherited from interface com.vmware.vcenter.hvc.management.AdministratorsTypes
